msgstr "ອັບເດດແລ້ວ %u ແອັບ — ຕ້ອງເລີ່ມໃໝ່"

#. TRANSLATORS: apps were auto-updated
#: src/gs-update-monitor.c:389
#, c-format
msgid "%u App Updated"
msgstr "ອັບເດດແລ້ວ %u ແອັບ"

